comments: Wiggins (MIN) makes contact to the body of Bembry (ATL) at the start of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Wiggins (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Collins' (ATL) shot attempt.
Young (ATL) has a resting arm and does not extend it into the body of Jones (MIN) during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Rose (MIN) makes incidental contact to the arm of Bembry (ATL) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact with Bembry (ATL) as he rolls to the basket.
Carter (ATL) cleanly deflects the basketball away from Rose (MIN) on his shot attempt, any additional contact from Bembry (ATL) is deemed incidental.
Towns (MIN) make marginal contact with Collins' (ATL) shoulder that does not affect his ability to rebound the ball.
Carter (ATL) makes contact to the arm of Towns (MIN) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Towns (MIN) briefly places his arm on Collins' (ATL) hip prior to the pick.
Collins (ATL) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Wiggins (MIN) while setting the pick.
[Observable in enhanced video] Rose (MIN) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball on the pass.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact when he screens and re-screens Bembry (ATL).
Collins (ATL) makes marginal contact to the body of Rose (MIN) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Collins (ATL) is firming up in a legal stance and delivers slight contact to Okogie (MIN) while setting the pick.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental contact to the body of Young (ATL) after his shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) and Carter (ATL) makes marginal contact with one another prior to the screen being set.
Bembry (ATL) makes marginal contact with Rose (MIN) during his drive to the basket.
Collins (ATL) moves towards the basket and briefly engages with Gibson (MIN) on the screen.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of no basket was confirmed.
As Spellman (ATL) rolls to the basket, he makes marginal contact with Jones (MIN).
Spellman (ATL) places two hands on Jones' (MIN) body and affects his defensive position as he disengages from the pick.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental contact to the arm of Bembry (ATL) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental leg to leg contact with Young (ATL) after setting the pick.
Okogie (MIN) does not make contact with the ball on the shot attempt.
Carter (ATL) makes incidental contact with Okogie's (MIN) body during the rebound.
Okogie (MIN) makes incidental contact with Spellman (ATL) after the two engage with one another during the rebound.
Wiggins (MIN) commits a take foul on Huerter (ATL).
Saric (MIN) commits a take foul on Carter (ATL).
Young (ATL) commits a take foul on Jones (MIN).
[Observable in enhanced video] Tolliver (MIN) lifts his pivot foot.
Towns (MIN) and Huerter (ATL) make marginal contact with one another during the rebound.
Okogie (MIN) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Towns (MIN) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
